title: Boston Bluebikes Visualization
description: An interactive Mapbox + D3 visualization showing real-time Bluebikes traffic across Boston. Features time filtering, traffic flow colors, and a custom legend.

title: What Determines Victory in League of Legends?
description: An interactive D3-based explorable explanation analyzing early-game advantages in professional League of Legends. Features a clickable Rift map, dynamic win-rate visualizations, and a logistic regression simulator for predicting victory.
